summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a deed from Assunta Desimone, individually and Rainier National Bank, Harold S. Shefelman, Mondo Desimone and rose D. Maselli as co-trustees under the last will and Testament of Giuseppe Desimone, deceased, for a portion of E. Hanford's Donation Claim in Section 9, Township 24 North, 4 East, W.M., King County, Washington for general municipal purposes.
